title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 21 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 21 2022
description:
Dictator Trudeau won't give up tyrannical powers. Putin recognizes breakaway Ukrainian regions. Male swimmer wins 4 Ivy League female titles. C&B analyze Putin's statement on Ukraine as it happens. Buck gives theories on what this really means. As for Biden, Clay says: "How would the Biden administration respond to this? They probably would let Russia, in theory, take this small region of eastern Ukraine and then hope that this thing just goes away."
